{"tid":843353,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"視察高鐵站　馬時亨不憂客源　反擔心7年後15條車軌太少","createTime":"2018-10-01T05:46:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-01T18:02:09.000Z","uid":39464,"like":2,"dislike":74,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"0db04557a7e17c1fdc2ccf514981d83174760beb","tid":843353,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T05:46:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20181001/s00001/cc08bca1b084596ea9525d59b6b415fa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20181001%2Fs00001%2Fcc08bca1b084596ea9525d59b6b415fa.jpg&h=fd9fa1b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n又到「十一黃金周」，港鐵主席馬時亨今早到高鐵西九龍站視察運作情況。他接受傳媒訪問時，預計黃金周期間，高鐵站每日會有6萬乘客經高鐵來港，將會是高鐵站啟用8天以來的高峰。對有關預測仍與政府早前預期的日均客量8萬人次要少，馬時亨直言「客源是要儲的」，反而擔心未來7年或10年後有人說「這站太小，15條車軌不夠多」。<br />\n<br />\n馬時亨表示，對於預期每日班次減至約80班，是因為需要彈性處理車務狀況。他又稱港鐵一直與中國鐵路總公司（鐵總）有聯繫，加上西九站剛新開，希望以乘客獲得最舒適的體驗為依歸，故決定減少班次。他說：「前一陣子很多傳媒朋友都說我們不夠人，如果不夠人，開車開得多也不是太好。」<br />\n<br />\n他稱，今日看到無論售票或候車大堂都很暢順，人龍問題已解決，西九站開了8日，運作上有進步，這也是他們期望看到的。<br />\n<br />\n被問及客量是否未達預期時，馬時亨表示：「好多事都要習慣。有些朋友一開始會不習慣（乘搭高鐵），但坐過後都表示自己要搭高鐵了，客源是要儲的。」他又說，往後港鐵及旅行社均有推廣計劃，故不擔心客源問題，「我反而擔心7年或10年後有人說這站太小，15條車軌不夠多」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181001/s00001/1538370307764\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181001%2Fs00001%2F1538370307764&d=bBl8EthJxyjD0h9sAt%2BBkiwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=d183d727\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181001%2Fs00001%2F1538370307764&h=d02fdd0b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181001/s00001/1538370307764</a>"},{"pid":"84fa17a1408f5032c9e87e6037d82288962713f1","tid":843353,"uid":45185,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T05:47:09.000Z","msg":"有份交稅既死左都會去搵佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9b5264e738f6193d12715ac37970ee9a7b8738d","tid":843353,"uid":204736,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T05:47:46.000Z","msg":"未洗劫夠庫房就真<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"702c8de3a8e6d0607bdcfa5b6c58063d8859470e","tid":843353,"uid":73269,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"84fa17a1408f5032c9e87e6037d82288962713f1","tid":843353,"uid":45185,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T05:47:09.000Z","msg":"有份交稅既死左都會去搵佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T05:47:48.000Z","msg":"佢都就快死"},{"pid":"4e5864167ca8c9a7fe6b3a8975d425d76720609e","tid":843353,"uid":133806,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T05:48:23.000Z","msg":"又係呀<br />\n遲下玩下手咁多支那難民列車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bad1f7238f776b3e727f3182799a285665821967","tid":843353,"uid":190540,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T05:48:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"41c0cbbfdd3f28fa85b7dbace6a27ae4ed37b194","tid":843353,"uid":134323,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T05:52:44.000Z","msg":"點解當年生 cancer 死唔去"},{"pid":"f2e2294511721e212f95be5e0ca57a0c59c1c7c1","tid":843353,"uid":54337,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T05:52:53.000Z","msg":"15條軌，運兵仲唔夠？"},{"pid":"b27f3f0317cfa27dc00786447ab6e78d0e683722","tid":843353,"uid":192190,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T05:53:13.000Z","msg":"馬時亨: 7年後蝕到港人想死, 擔心15條車軌太少唔夠俾港人跳軌"},{"pid":"6b58e51e62d0fb09dbc22216fb88fa41e0b696f4","tid":843353,"uid":132587,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T05:54:07.000Z","msg":"我都好擔心你七年之後仲係唔係度<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ed0f5d3eb0214d48c23f898944dca5cf83566c4","tid":843353,"uid":3629